#, fuzzy
msgid "Events are fired asynchronously. Use `@ObservesAsync` (not `@Observes`) to receive them."
msgstr "Los eventos se activan de forma asíncrona. Utilice `@ObservesAsync` (y no `@Observes` ) para recibirlos."

#. type: Plain text
